# TrueCrypt

Truecrypt is a open source disk encryption software and it is recommended to use it to store sensitive data like passwords.

If you are using simple notepad file to store your username/password for internal usage at Serverpoint.com then you must use Truecrypt to create disk encryption.

Go to Truecrypt website and download latest version and install.
